lead_paragraph: Canada has rejected more than 72,000 applications from people seeking Indian status, the latest turn in a chaotic process to decide who in Newfoundland qualifies as a Native Canadian.

headline.main: Many Apply, Few Qualify: Canada Rejects Indian Status for Thousands
